0:01:52.920,0:01:57.940
Emanueri! (Mwari Anesu - Mateu 1:23)

0:01:57.940,0:02:01.220
Zita rangu ndi Joy Gersak. Ini ndinobva ku Austria.

0:02:01.220,0:02:02.780
Ndinotenda Mwari.

0:02:02.780,0:02:07.020
Munhu wose anofanira kundibatsira kutenda munhu Mwari nekundidzosa kuupenyu.

0:02:07.020,0:02:08.700
Ndakanga ndichitambura zvechokwadi.

0:02:08.700,0:02:12.960
Ndakanga ndichipfuura nemumarwadzo kubva pane oparesheni imwe kuenda kune imwe.

0:02:12.960,0:02:18.140
Zuva rimwe nerimwe - mapiritsi, vanachiremba uye kubva kuna chiremba umwe kuenda kune umwe.

0:02:18.140,0:02:24.900
Vakataura kuti waiva mutambo - nekuda kwemitambo ndicho chikonzero nei ndairwadziwa

0:02:24.900,0:02:29.920
Ndakamuka rimwe zuva ndikaona gumbo rangu rakanga rakazvimba.

0:02:29.920,0:02:31.760
Vaifanira kundimhanyisa kuchipatara.

0:02:31.760,0:02:34.100
Pandakasvika ikoko, vakati chaive ichi ne icho.

0:02:34.100,0:02:36.700
Vakanga vasingazivi chaizvo zvaiitika kwandiri.

0:02:36.700,0:02:40.020
Vakanga vachiti yaiva arthritis yebvi kana hurwa.

0:02:40.020,0:02:41.980
Ndakaenda kune chiremba uyu neuyo.

0:02:41.980,0:02:44.800
Ndakatora mapiritsi anopfuura 13 zuva rega rega.

0:02:44.800,0:02:49.940
Ndakanga ndavhiringidzika kusvika pakuvhiya kwekupedzisira, oparesheni yechipfumbamwe.

0:02:49.940,0:02:54.680
Yechipfumbamwe ndipo pakavaisa simbi; munhu wose anokwanisa kuiona.

0:02:54.680,0:02:57.080
Ndiyoyi.

0:02:57.080,0:03:02.140
Iyi ndeye chigumi; ivo vakati vaida kuisa imwe simbi.

0:03:02.140,0:03:09.960
Apa ndipo pavaibuditsa mvura napo katatu pasvondo.

0:03:09.960,0:03:14.080
Aiva mukoma wangu kubva ku Canada; Mwari amuropafadze.

0:03:14.080,0:03:16.760
Ndiye iye akabhadhara tikiti rangu kuti ndiuye panzvimbo ino.

0:03:16.760,0:03:17.980
Pandakasvika pano ...

0:03:17.980,0:03:19.880
Zvakanaka, musati maenda mberi madhamu ...

0:03:19.880,0:03:25.040
Tiri kuona kuti hanzvadzi yedu irikukurirwa kwazvo neuchapupu hwakanakisisa hwaanofanira kugovera.

0:03:25.040,0:03:32.080
Tinoda kuti iwe utsanangure zvakajeka; wakanga uine nguva yakareba sei une marwadzo e bilateral knee arthritis?

0:03:32.080,0:03:36.440
Tsanangura kwatiri; iwe wataura zve majekiseni, mapiritsi ...

0:03:36.440,0:03:41.440
Zuva nezuva, marwadzo hwai awaive unawo nekuda kwedambudziko iri?

0:03:41.440,0:03:43.180
Marwadzo akanyanyisa.

0:03:43.180,0:03:45.780
Handigoni kurangarira uye handidi kuzviyeuka.

0:03:45.780,0:03:47.140
Handigoni.

0:03:47.140,0:03:49.320
Handaikwanisa kudya kana kurara.

0:03:49.320,0:03:51.660
Ndaifanira kutora mapiritsi ndisati ndaenda kunorara.

0:03:51.660,0:03:55.080
Ndisati ndabva pamubhedha, ndaitora mapiritsi.

0:03:55.080,0:03:59.640
Ndezvipi zvinhu zvawakanga usingakwanisi kuita zvachose nekuda kwezvese izvi?

0:03:59.640,0:04:03.680
Handaikwanisa kufamba; Ndakarega kushanda.

0:04:03.680,0:04:06.680
Ndakanga ndisingakwanisi kuita chero zvaiitwa nevamwe vangu.

0:04:06.680,0:04:07.700
Kwete saizvozvo.

0:04:07.700,0:04:09.160
Dzimwe nguva kunyange kuenda ku chimbuzi ..

0:04:09.160,0:04:10.720
Uyu mwanasikana wangu mukuru.

0:04:10.720,0:04:14.560
Vadiki vacho zvakare, vaifanira kundiendesa kuchimbuzi nokundidzosa.

0:04:14.560,0:04:16.000
Fungidzira!

0:04:16.000,0:04:20.720
Ndakanga ndichipfuura nemumarwadzo.

0:04:20.720,0:04:24.720
Iwe wati wakapfuura ne muma opareshini mangani usati wauya pano?

0:04:24.720,0:04:26.180
Ma opareshini mapfumbamwe.

0:04:26.180,0:04:31.100
Ma oparesheni mapfumbamwe; kusvika kumwero wekuti simbi yakaiswa mune rimwe ramabvi ako?

0:04:31.100,0:04:32.400
Hongu.

0:04:32.400,0:04:37.360
Vakanga vakuudza kuti vaida kuisa simbi mune rimwe ibvi, usati wasvika pano?

0:04:37.360,0:04:39.260
Hongu, uye ivo vakati ini handina kodzero yekuzvisarudzira.

0:04:39.260,0:04:41.020
Vaifanira kundisarudzira.

0:04:41.020,0:04:49.260
Saka, vakasarudza ndokuronga zuva re musi wa November 6 kuti ndipe zvakawanikwa muropa rangu nezvose.

0:04:49.260,0:04:51.660
Ndakauya pano musi wa 3 November.

0:04:51.660,0:04:54.660
Wakaziva sei pamusoro pezve SCOAN?

0:04:54.660,0:04:59.760
Iwe wakanga uri padanho rakakosha zvikuru ikozvino, vaida kukuopareta rimwe ibvi uye kuisa simbi ...

0:04:59.760,0:05:01.260
Zvakaitika sei kuti iwe uvepano?

0:05:01.260,0:05:06.720
Yaiva shamwari; iye anopfuura mukoma kwandiri uye ari ku Canada.

0:05:06.720,0:05:10.060
Ndiye akatsigira kuuya kwangu panzvimbo ino.

0:05:10.060,0:05:11.300
Tinotenda Mwari Wamasimbaose.

0:05:11.300,0:05:12.860
Pawakasvika pano ...

0:05:12.860,0:05:17.620
Tapupurira pasikirini zviitiko zvakaitika apo mu Porofita T.B. Joshua akakunyengeterera.

0:05:17.620,0:05:22.560
Unogona here kutsanangura kwatiri chaizvo zvakaitika, apo munhu wa Mwari akatanga kunyengetera?

0:05:22.560,0:05:25.340
Apo munhu wa Mwari aindinyengeterera, ndakafenda.

0:05:25.340,0:05:29.940
Handigoni kuyeuka zvainge zvichiitika.

0:05:29.940,0:05:34.360
Chinhu chimwe chete chandakanzwa ndechekuti, "Simuka ufambe" ndakabva ndakatanga kumhanya.

0:05:34.360,0:05:36.680
Ndicho chega chinhu chandinoyeuka.

0:05:36.680,0:05:41.240
Zvakanaka, ngatiisei maoko edu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:05:41.240,0:05:46.260
Apo munhu wa Mwari ainge achinyengetera, achitaura nendimi, muviri wako wose waiva uchizunguzika nekudedera;

0:05:46.260,0:05:47.860
