0:05:47.860,0:05:50.280
Kana kana.

0:05:50.280,0:05:54.900
Nguva yawakanzwa chiziviso chekuti, "Simuka ufambe!", Chii chakaitika?

0:05:54.900,0:05:59.880
Ndakanga ndasununguka uye ndakanga ndisisanzwi kurwadziwa zvakare.

0:05:59.880,0:06:05.900
Ndakarara semucheche - pasina mapiritsi pasina majekiseni.

0:06:05.900,0:06:11.460
Wawu, ngatiisei maoko edu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:06:11.460,0:06:14.600
Pane mutsauko mukuru, mukuru kwazvo.

0:06:14.600,0:06:19.520
Kare, ndakanga ndisingagoni kufamba kana kuita zvaiitwa ne vamwe vangu.

0:06:19.520,0:06:22.980
Asi mushure mokudzokera kwangu, zvinhu zvose zvakanga zvakanaka.

0:06:22.980,0:06:24.760
Ndinogona kuita zvose.

0:06:24.760,0:06:26.120
Ndakatangawo kushanda.

0:06:26.120,0:06:28.840
Ini ndinoshanda ikozvino, nepo kare, ndakanga ndisingakwanisi kushanda.

0:06:28.840,0:06:32.900
Ndakanga ndiri pamudya ndigere se munhu akarega basa.

0:06:32.900,0:06:36.480
Pandakadzokera kuAustria, ndakadzokera kuna chiremba.

0:06:36.480,0:06:41.040
Chiremba akaongorora zvose uye akati zvose zvaive zvakanaka; saka, ndakatanga kushanda.

0:06:41.040,0:06:42.400
Iye zvino, ndinoshanda.

0:06:42.400,0:06:46.020
Zvakanaka, ngatiisei maoko edu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:06:46.020,0:06:50.820
Imi manga mataura madhamu kuti vanachiremba vakanga vakubhukai kuti muitwe oparesheni.

0:06:50.820,0:06:53.800
Pamakadzokera kunyika yenyu - Austria, chii chakaitika?

0:06:53.800,0:07:01.920
Pandakadzokera kuAustria, ndakaenda kunosangana nachiremba wangu ndikamuudza kuti ndaida kutorwa x-ray, iyo yandakatorwa.

0:07:01.920,0:07:06.860
Apo chiremba akaongorora, akandibvunza zvandakanga ndaita negumbo rangu.

0:07:06.860,0:07:10.160
Ndakati, "Uyu ndi Mwari" iye akati, "Mwari, Mwari chii?"

0:07:10.160,0:07:13.580
Ndakamuudza kuti ndakanga ndaenda ku Nigeria kuchechi kunonamata.

0:07:13.580,0:07:17.420
Akataura kuti hakuna Mwari asi ini ndakati, " Mwari ariko".

0:07:17.420,0:07:21.420
Akati haakwanisa kuwana chero chinhu mugumbo rangu kuti aoparete pariri saka vaisakwanisa kuopareta.

0:07:21.420,0:07:26.960
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu!

0:07:26.960,0:07:33.960
Ichi chipatara chakanga chataurira hanzvadzi yedu kuti vaifanira kuisa simbi mune rimwe ibvi rake

0:07:33.960,0:07:41.080
nekuda kwekuoma kwe arthritis yaive mairi, asi chipatara chimwechete chakaongorora x-ray chikasimbisa

0:07:41.080,0:07:42.180
