0:07:42.180,0:07:44.300
Akanga asingafaniri kuenda kunoitwa oparesheni.

0:07:44.300,0:07:52.680
Ndanga ndisiri kutora mapiritsi, majekiseni, rubatsiro kana kuona vanachiremba.

0:07:52.680,0:07:54.740
Ndinokutendai, Jesu!

0:07:54.740,0:07:58.480
Kupa kubwinya kuna Mwari; tinongoda kuti iwe uratidze kuti wakugona kufamba zvakasununguka ikozvino,

0:07:58.480,0:08:04.760
mushure memunyengetero wawakagamuchira.

0:08:04.760,0:08:10.500
Wawu, uyu munhu aifanira kuzvibaya jekiseni kuti angogona kufamba zvishoma.

0:08:10.500,0:08:12.660
Tirikuona zvaari kuita izvozvi.

0:08:12.660,0:08:13.940
Imi murikunzwa sei, madhamu?

0:08:13.940,0:08:20.360
Ndiri kunzwa zvakanaka ikozvino; Ndinofunga kuti ndinogona kudzokera kumitambo!

0:08:20.360,0:08:21.940
Wawu, Ndinokutendai, Jesu Kristu!

0:08:21.940,0:08:26.700
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kamwe zvakare kuna Ishe wedu Jesu Kristu.

0:08:26.700,0:08:31.760
Madhamu, tirikuona manzwiranyaya ezvekurapwa kubva kunachiremba pabhodhi apa, pamwe ne x-ray.

0:08:31.760,0:08:38.300
Zvakanaka, iyi itsanangudzo yezvekurapwa, apo chiremba akati zvinhu zvose zvakanaka negumbo rangu.

0:08:38.300,0:08:40.520
Handifanirwe kuitwa chero oparesheni.

0:08:40.520,0:08:42.820
Zvakanyorwa muchi Dutch.

0:08:42.820,0:08:44.900
Tinotenda Jesu Kristu.

0:08:44.900,0:08:50.480
Tsanangudzo yezvekurapwa yakanyatsonyorwa muchi German, asi hanzvadzi yedu iri kutsanangura kuti vanachiremba

0:08:50.480,0:08:55.600
vakanga vasimbisa kuti akanga asisade kuenda kundovhiyiwa pabvi rake, sezvaaiva

0:08:55.600,0:08:58.280
aporeswa zvakakwana, mbiri kuna Mwari Wamasimba Ose.

0:08:58.280,0:09:00.680
Tinokwanisawo kuona zvakare x-ray pano.

0:09:00.680,0:09:02.680
Mungagone here kuratidza izvi kwatiri, madhamu?

0:09:02.680,0:09:09.880
Iyi ndiwo x-ray yebvi rangu reruboshwe kare.

0:09:09.880,0:09:14.320
Iyi ndiyo x-ray yebvi rangu, ravaida kuvhiya.

0:09:14.320,0:09:15.580
Zvino, zvinhu zvose zvakanaka.

0:09:15.580,0:09:19.980
Apa ndipo pavaibvisa mvura napo kare.

0:09:19.980,0:09:21.920
Kubvira ipapo, vakarega kubuditsa mvura.

0:09:21.920,0:09:27.440
Kare, vaizobuditsa mvura katatu pavhiki.

0:09:27.440,0:09:29.440
Handina marwadzo zvakare.

0:09:29.440,0:09:34.120
Ichi ndicho chishamiso chikuru uye tinopa kubwinya kose kuna Ishe wedu Jesu Kristu;

0:09:34.120,0:09:40.860
kamwe zvakare, vanhu va Mwari, ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu nekununura hanzvadzi yedu

0:09:40.860,0:09:44.220
ne kumusunungura zvachose - tinotenda Ishe wedu Jesu Kristu.

0:09:44.220,0:09:48.600
Madhamu, ikozvino, sezvo muri pano nhasi, muri kurarama, muchifamba, munotaura chishamiso kune uchapupu

0:09:48.600,0:09:50.020
hwa Ishe wedu Jesu Kristu;

0:09:50.020,0:09:53.720
Yambiro yenyu kune vatariri pasi rose inoti kudii?

0:09:53.720,0:09:59.540
Yambiro yangu kune umwe neumwe ari kundiona iye zvino ndeyekuti

0:09:59.540,0:10:03.500
kana uine dambudziko, ndapota, usarasikirwa netariro; tizira kuna Mwari.

0:10:03.500,0:10:11.300
Ndakaenda kunzvimbo dzakawanda ndikaparadza mari asi ndakauya pano asi munhu wa Mwari haana kutora chero mari kubva kwandiri.

0:10:11.300,0:10:14.040
Apo ndakanga ndichidzokera, ndinoziva zvaakandipa.

0:10:14.040,0:10:18.300
Akandipa zvinhu zvakawanda, kusanganisira ne Morning Water.

0:10:18.300,0:10:20.160
Munhu wose anofanira kundibatsira kutenda munhu wa Mwari.

0:10:20.160,0:10:24.580
Zano rangu nderekuti kana uine matambudziko, mhanya kuna Mwari.

0:10:24.580,0:10:25.920
Ndiko kwandakawana rugare rwangu.

0:10:25.920,0:10:29.660
Pano ndipo pandichange ndichiuya nguva dzose, muzita ra Jesu.

0:10:29.660,0:10:32.080
Ameni. Ndinokutendai, Jesu Kristu.

0:10:32.080,0:10:33.720
Zita rangu ndiDeborah.

0:10:33.720,0:10:35.300
Ava ndi mai vangu.

0:10:35.300,0:10:39.000
Vasati vasvika pachechi, vakanga vane kurwadziwa kwakanyanya.

0:10:39.000,0:10:46.560
Ini ne munin'ina wangu taifanira kusuka ndiro; kutsvaira mumba, kuwacha nhumbi ne kuvabatsira muzuva rose.

