0:10:53.780,0:10:57.780
Kwaingova kusuka ndiro, kuwacha ne mabasa epamba, hapana chimwe chinhu.

0:10:57.780,0:11:00.520
Taisakwanisa kubvisa marwadzo kwavari.

0:11:00.520,0:11:02.860
Amai vako vakauya ku SCOAN.

0:11:02.860,0:11:09.320
Ndezvipi zvakachinja, shanduko yawakaona pavakadzokera kuAustria ndeipi?

0:11:09.320,0:11:15.040
Takaona kuti vaigona kuita zvinhu zvavaisagona kuita kare.

0:11:15.040,0:11:20.700
Vave kukwanisa kufamba chinhambwe chirefu uye kunotenga.

0:11:20.700,0:11:28.860
Ini ne munin'ina wangu taigona kuisa pfungwa dzedu pane zvidzidzo zvedu uye kuenda kumwe kakakwanda.

0:11:28.860,0:11:33.240
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu kamwe zvakare.

0:11:33.240,0:11:39.200
Zano rangu nderekuti: munhu wose anofanira kutenda; usarasikirwa nerutendo muna Mwari.

0:11:39.200,0:11:40.060
Ndinokutendai, Jesu.

0:11:40.060,0:11:42.640
Tinotenda Mwari Wemasimbaose nokuda kwechishamiso ichi chakanakisisa.

0:11:42.640,0:11:48.700
Tinonyengeterera kuti Mwari ape hanzvadzi dzedu dziri pano nyasha dzekuramba dzichichengeta

0:11:48.700,0:11:53.600
chinhu chakanakisisa chavakagamuchira kubva kwa Ari uye kuita Shoko ra Mwari nhungamiro yeupenyu hwavo

0:11:53.600,0:11:59.240
uye sezvavanoita saizvozvo, tinoziva, zviri nani hazvina kukwana - zvakanakisisa zvichiri kuuya, muzita ra Jesu.

